version_description: Added Transcribed Intro Riff (Floydman939) to Chords (MatisyahuFan). Thanks to the original Tabbers.
Includes chords for all parts and diagrams for special inversions.
This madness is brought to you by Puddles Pity Party on YouTube (among others): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6bfPwtUTP4k.
Complete and well-aligned chords for vocal and instrumental parts / two versions: with and without capo / suggestions for special voicings.
The previously existing versions have incorrect chords and bad formatting.
